      "message": "ok, then I\u0027m not sure what\u0027s going on. Since the virtualscene camera code and this code are using some common pieces, perhaps we can try to compare? E.g., for a given camera in the guest, it has some resolution W x H, and virtualscene will have W1 x H1 and the rendering here will have W2 x H2. Presumably, all 3 are the same numbers.\n\nwe can also do a local test with glReadPixels mRenderWidth mRenderHeight to see if that agrees.",
